            <h2>Wait...What’s EMV?</h2>
        </header>
        <p>EMV stands for Europay, Mastercard®, and Visa®, and is the gold standard of payment transaction processing for most of the world. This year, EMV chip cards – credit cards with small microchips embedded in them - are coming to the U.S. EMV improves payment security by making it harder to use cards fraudulently or even duplicate them.</p>
